  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>Get the skills you need to become a financial team leader, set up your own practice or enter the second year of a degree programme.</p>
<p>AAT qualifications are held in high regard in the financial sector both at home and abroad. AAT Level 4 covers statements for limited companies and complex management accounting tasks.</p>]]></mainContent>
