                      "text": "<h2>What could I do next?</h2>\n<p>AAT is a brand that employers trust because its qualifications demonstrate that you have the practical real world skills to be successful within business and finance. Financial management is at the heart of every business, so demand for Accounting and Finance skills is consistently high across all sectors.</p>\n<p>On successful completion your options will include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Earning straight away in a Business or Finance role</li>\n<li>Studying to become a Chartered Accountant</li>\n<li>Entering the second year of a degree programme at university</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You will also automatically become an AAT Affiliate Member and, if you have relevant work experience, can qualify for a full AAT membership.</p>",
